annotationA: Eukaryotic initiation factor 1A, isoform A; Seems to be required for maximal rate of protein biosynthesis. Enhances ribosome dissociation into subunits and stabilizes the binding of the initiator Met-tRNA(I) to 40 S ribosomal subunits
annotationB: Ribosomal protein S7; Belongs to the eukaryotic ribosomal protein eS7 family
